 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utugurok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tugurok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/15/02 10:14:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=629.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pantheon.yale.edu/~bdiebold/images/TugReal.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Has Venril Sathir gotten harder over time?</span><hr size=1> Are you sure you aren't thinking about Venril Sathir's Remains? VSR is doable pretty easily by 1 or 2 good groups, while VS himself is a bit tougher. 1500 point lifetaps are a pain.<br><br> <p><p><A href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76073><img border="0" src="http://members.glaznor.org/signature/tugurok.jpg"</A></p><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utamria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tamria</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/02 1:14:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=629.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Has Venril Sathir gotten harder over time?</span><hr size=1> To two-group him with sub-60's you'd need a lot of DPS, his lifetap tends to get through a fair bit even with runing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2