ttp://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=629.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Has Venril Sathir gotten harder over time?</span><hr size=1> /agree Coray<br><br>Change your tactics for the real VS<br><br>One war, one cleric, one chanter, 3 damage tanks and 3 wizzes are enough to down the real VS (avg levels 56-8)  if you do it in a way where he can't tap you. Tap is a proc. Think about it a bit and you will see.<br><br>As far as runes go: The runes used to block the tap. He would tap, get no HP and would only eat the rune. After patch the system remains the same except VS himself heals from the tap as if you did not have a rune on.<br><br>Subb <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usubbiano.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Subbiano</A> at: 3/19/02 2:19:38 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugobbfromluclin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gobb from Luclin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 10:41:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=629.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Has Venril Sathir gotten harder over time?</span><hr size=1> Have only done real VS once.  You absolutely must get all melees behind VS because he ripostes madly, and when he does, he almost always life taps you for 1500.  If peeps are in front of him, he won't die, he'll just suck you all dry.  Good idea to get a rune on all melee present anyway, to take care of any accidents.<br><br>Could be a good idea to debuff his dexi too to mitigate the rate he procs at.  Can't remember if he was slowable. <p>Rev. Gobb Heartrender 55 Troll 